{"tid":2492104,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣家旻化身「貧乳」波多野莎莎玩SM緊縳    孖張秀文下海拍AV","createTime":"2021-04-16T23:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T23:42:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7a561b3e6a4ad6e6c3ac37212870674b631f72","tid":2492104,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:42:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/entertainment/欺詐劇團-蔣家旻-張秀文-plt-1129329/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2Fentertainment%2F%E6%AC%BA%E8%A9%90%E5%8A%87%E5%9C%98-%E8%94%A3%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%BB-%E5%BC%B5%E7%A7%80%E6%96%87-plt-1129329%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=9a5d8aa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.weekendhk.com/entertainment/欺詐劇團-蔣家旻-張秀文-plt-1129329/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/heift_195384794560780f290312a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fheift_195384794560780f290312a.jpeg&h=7a79828b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔣家旻孖張秀文下海「拍AV」，於新劇《欺詐劇團》化身「AV女優」！劇中蔣家旻飾演編劇，不過應邀客串飾演「貧乳波多野莎莎」，家旻更要穿上性感肚兜，慘被五花大綁倒吊，十足十AV情節<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/-2021-04-15-1.25.35_14330654166077e48fdb5b6-1024x882.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F-2021-04-15-1.25.35_14330654166077e48fdb5b6-1024x882.png&h=2b43888b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/-2021-04-15-1.30.37_21130503856077e50f3fe68-1024x729.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F-2021-04-15-1.30.37_21130503856077e50f3fe68-1024x729.png&h=7b57de20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔣家旻 張秀文下海「拍AV」 無綫新劇《欺詐劇團》將於本周五（16日）在myTV Gold播出，蔣家旻與張秀文將化身「AV女優」齊齊下海「拍AV」！劇中蔣家旻飾演編劇，為了欺騙男主角，犧牲色相扮女優，應邀客串飾演「波多野莎莎」，穿上性感肚兜，更慘被五花大綁倒吊，十足十日本AV片情節，題材踩界。日前蔣家旻帶同道具影碟宣傳新劇《欺詐劇團》，連「AV」封面照也認真製作，印着「貧乳美少女」、「巨根」等字眼，問到家旻覺唔覺得自己「貧乳」？她笑言：「秀文太好身材，咁我覺得自己都OK嘅！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/-2021-04-15-1.25.33-_16603847836077e5f55a0f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F-2021-04-15-1.25.33-_16603847836077e5f55a0f0.png&h=34a58c9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/-2021-04-15-1.26.27-2_8396144736077f46e2d5c2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F-2021-04-15-1.26.27-2_8396144736077f46e2d5c2.png&h=82b28a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/gl_15847286186077be1f6da67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fgl_15847286186077be1f6da67.jpg&h=93967484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/km_18318098816077be2204824-696x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fkm_18318098816077be2204824-696x1024.jpg&h=4b2c9393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/m1_18267876326077be25610fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fm1_18267876326077be25610fd.jpg&h=5e7c58aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n秀文化身「新世代美巨乳D cup」女優 至於張秀文就化身另一AV女優，最強素人「玲奈子」，秀文穿上性感內衣拍攝影碟封面照，碟面則寫上「新世代美巨乳D cup」、「3P」、「中出」等露骨字眼，但秀文豪不介意，更大讚道具製作認真，被問到是否真的擁有D Cup身材？她就扭扭擰擰說︰「32D囉，今次真係近期最性感一次，因為我會不停縮沙，唔會好似以前咁性感。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-conten